'''Galactic Power Brokers''' is an article appearing in [[Star Wars Gamer 10|''Star Wars Gamer'' 10]]. It gave a brief description and stats for several powerful individuals in the ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[The galaxy/Legends|galaxy]], including [[Senator/Legends|Senators]] [[Mas Amedda/Legends|Mas Amedda]], [[Bail Prestor Organa/Legends|Bail Organa]] and [[Orn Free Taa/Legends|Orn Free Taa]]; [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatists]] [[Shu Mai/Legends|Shu Mai]], [[Nute Gunray/Legends|Nute Gunray]], [[Passel Argente/Legends|Passel Argente]], [[Wat Tambor/Legends|Wat Tambor]] and [[San Hill/Legends|San Hill]]; and underworld power brokers [[Elan Sel'Sabagno/Legends|Elan Sel'Sabagno]] and [[Dexter Jettster/Legends|Dexter Jettster]].<ref name="Gamer 10">[[Star Wars Gamer 10|''Star Wars Gamer'' 10]]</ref>

